(2, 'BUILT IN DISH WASHERS-Ariston-LIC 3B+26', '/uploads/product/main_image/2019-10-01/156992066988.png', '11299.00', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, '<h1 class=\"product__info__title\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; font-size: 3em; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.1; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">Ariston Built-In Dishwasher, 14 Place Settings, 60 cm, White - LIC 3B+26</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h1 class=\"product__info__title\" style=\"line-height: 1.1; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; font-size: 3em; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 80, 86); font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">14 Place Settings, With a large 14 place settings capacity, you can wash all of your dishes, even larger items, in one go.</span><strong><span dir=\"LTR\"> </span></strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 80, 86); font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">Half load Program, For loading half the table settings distributed among the various racks, while ensuring the same washing efficacy with reduced consumption.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 80, 86); font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">Delicates Program, Its low temperature prevents thermal shocks from damaging glassware and crystal items.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 80, 86); font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">ECO Program, The wash cycle to which the energy label data refers, the most efficient in terms of consumption for normally soiled tableware.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 8