(34, 'HOODS-Ariston-SL 16.1 (WH)', '/uploads/product/main_image/2019-10-01/15699261257.png', '1999.00', NULL, NULL, 1, 1, '<p>Ariston suction 60 cm-suction power: 385 m3 / hour-3 speeds for suction-2 filters of aluminium</p>\r\n\r\n<p>About the product<br />\r\nIf you&rsquo;re after a basic cooker hood to remove any lingering smells from your kitchen, the Ariston Visor Hood is your choice. Offering 3 extraction speeds, you can use the lowest level for soup you might have simmering and the highest for flash frying steaks. This model has 2 self-supporting aluminum filters that will keep any pesky grease out of the air and off your clothes. Plus, there are 2 halogen lights that will help you see when you&rsquo;re chopping up ingredients.<br />\r\nFeatures We Love&nbsp;<br />\r\n3 Different Speeds This model has three extraction speeds to choose from, so it&rsquo;s great for clearing the air in your kitchen quickly. Select the lowest setting when you&rsquo;re simmering or steaming food and the highest setting for frying and strong-smelling food.<br />\r\nSuitable For 60 cm Hobs When you&rsquo;re looking for a cooker hood to suit your kitchen space, you want to make sure that it&rsquo;s the right size. This model would look fantastic above a 60 cm wide hob making it ideal for a standard-sized kitchen.</p>', 'SL 16.1 (WH)', 6, 1, 100, '2019-10-01 14:35:25', '2019-10-03 17:52:22', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
