(59, 'OVENS-Ariston-MKG 23 (IX)', '/uploads/product/main_image/2019-10-01/1569928267348.png', '18699.00', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, '<p>Ariston&#39;s oven is 90 centimeters of gas with a fan and a digital electric grille, 97 liters stanliss</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">Useful, spacious and easy. With its stainless steel finish and easy to use knobs and buttons, the Ariston built-in gas oven - MKG 23 (IX) is easy to use. The 97 litres space means you&rsquo;ll have enough room to cook for 4 or 5 people.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: medium; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">97 Litres Gas Oven</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">With its 97 Litres capacity, cooking meals is made easy and effortless. Offering functionality, convenience, and control, this built-in oven is the perfect companion for your kitchen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: medium; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Distribution Fan For Better Cooking</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">Always achieve perfectly roasted meat and evenly baked desserts with the distribution fan in Ariston oven. the distribution fan allows the hot air goes throughout the oven for perfect, quick and even cooking results.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: medium; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Inner Glass Door</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">The inner door made from reinforced tempered glass offers a smooth surface, free from tiny openings or gaps in which dirt or grease tend to deposit, making cleaning easier and more efficient. The inner door also offers a safe rest surface when checking cooking progress or removing the dripping pan or the grill.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: medium; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Cooking Programs</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">The cooking programs are to make it easier for you to decide what type of food you want to cook. The settings provided greatly simplify your use of this oven to cook these foods. The available Cooking Programs are Grill, Traditional.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: medium; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Electric Grill</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">Healthier than other cooking methods, grilling your food seals in juices to offer delicious flavor, while browning your food at the same time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: medium; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Grey Cavity</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">The cavities of MKG 23 (IX) built-in oven improves visibility inside the oven during cooking, making it easier to check the progress of your dishes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: medium; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Safety Sensor</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">You don&#39;t have to worry while cooking. The oven is featured with a safety sensor the oven making it a completely safe use.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: medium; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">1 Grids, 1 Tray</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">There are 1 grid and 1 tray that you can use to simplify your cooking variations.</p>', 'MKG 23 (IX)', 5, 1, 100, '2019-10-01 15:11:07', '2019-10-08 14:33:48', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL);
