amily: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: medium; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Cooking Is Safe</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">Ariston FI5 851 C IX A&nbsp;built-in oven is equipped with an innovative safety device for completely safe use.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"smalltitle\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.1; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 7px; font-size: 1.4em; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: medium; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\">Multiflow Heat Technology</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"description\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">With Mulitiflow Technology, a new style of convection system creates an all-enveloping heat flow which drives heat into every inch of the oven cavity for consistently even, delicious dishes every time &ndash; whichever shelf you&#39;re using. Ideal for ensuring perfectly risen cakes and breads, as well as uniform cooking of your favorite dishes.</p>', 'FI5 851 C IX A', 5, 1, 100, '2019-10-01 15:13:45', '2019-10-08 15:12:40', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
