 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">Thanks to the strong fan located in the rear of the oven, heat is distributed evenly. This delivers the same cooking results at a traditional oven, in less time and saving energy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: medium; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">78 Litres Gas Oven</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">With its 78 Litres capacity, cooking meals is made easy and effortless. Offering functionality, convenience, and control, this built-in oven is the perfect companion for your kitchen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: medium; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Electric Grill</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">Healthier than other cooking methods, grilling your food seals in juices to offer delicious flavor, while browning your food at the same time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: medium; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Electronic Temperature Control</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">Electronic control minimizes swings in temperature during the cooking process, ensuring constant heat and a repeatable result every time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: medium; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Assisted Cycles</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">The semi-automatic cycles suggest essential cooking parameters and guide the user in the choice of best temperature and shelf setting for the food, for perfect results every time. The temperatures and cooking times suggested by the oven can easily be modified.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: medium; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Inner Glass Door</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">The inner door made from reinforced tempered glass offers a smooth surface, free from tiny openings or gaps in which dirt or grease tend to deposit, making cleaning easier and more efficient. The inner door also offers a safe rest surface when checking cooking progress or removing the dripping pan or the grill.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: medium; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">2 Grids, 1 Tray</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">There are 2 grid and 1 tray that you can use to simplify your cooking variations.</p>', 'ML 99 IX', 5, 1, 100, '2019-10-01 15:18:58', '2019-10-08 15:37:09', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
(68, 'OVENS-Ariston-FI7 871 SP IX A', '/uploads/product/main_image/2019-10-01/1569928785577.png', '16449.00', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, '<p>Ariston&#39;s oven is 60 centimetres electric, 73 liters digital touch, turbo-Pyrolitic stables fan</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">Useful, spacious and easy. With its stainless steel finish and easy to use mono knob and buttons, the Ariston built-in electric oven - FI7 871 SP IX A is easy to use. The 73 litres space means you&rsquo;ll have enough room to cook for 3 or 4 people.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: medium; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Multifunction Oven</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">Bake perfect cupcakes, roast your delicious dinner or use the grill to make a hearty but healthy breakfast! Ariston multifunction oven provides you with the ultimate in cooking flexibility by combining a fan and conventional oven, a grill and a host of different cooking functions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: medium; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Multiflow Heat Technology</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">With Mulitiflow Technology, a new style of convection system creates an all-enveloping heat flow which drives heat into every inch of the oven cavity for consistently even, delicious dishes every time &ndash; whichever shelf you&#39;re using. Ideal for ensuring perfectly risen cakes and bread, as well as uniform cooking of your favorite dishes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: medium; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Pyrolytic Cleaning system</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">The Ariston oven has two automatic pyrolytic cycles to suit the type of stains, needing no chemical products, thanks to the temperature of 470&deg; C that reduces the dirt to ash. The residue ash can then be easily removed using a damp cloth.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: medium; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">73 Litres Gas Oven</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">With its 73 Litres capacity, cooking meals is made easy and effortless. Offering functionality, convenience, and control, this built-in oven is the perfect companion for your kitchen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: medium; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Electronic Temperature Control</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">Electronic control minimizes swings in temperature during the cooking process, ensuring constant heat and a repeatable result every time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: medium; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Touch Control</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">The Ariston oven responds to the controls in an instant thanks to the special Touch Control system. To dialogue and interact with the oven is simple: just touch the few but beautifully clear icons and follow an intuitive sequence to obtain perfect and effortless cooking of any recipe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: medium; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Soft Closing</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">The soft closing is a system that uses new generation hinges to gently accompany the oven door, and prevent it from banging.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: medium; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Telescopic Guides</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">The Telescopic Guides are functional and practical for gliding and supporting the drip tray when it is removed from the oven, makes control even easier and safer while cooking.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: medium; color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">1 Grid, 1 Tray &amp; 1 Deep Tray</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 49px; font-size: 1.4em; color: rgb(64, 80, 86); line-height: 1.8; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">There are 1 grid, 1 tray and 1 deep tray that you can use to simplify your cooking variations.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>.</p>', 'FI7 871 SP IX A', 5, 1, 100, '2019-10-01 15:19:45', '2019-10-08 15:38:23', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL);
