(105, 'Dryers-Ariston-TCF 97B 6XX1 (EX)', '/uploads/product/main_image/2019-10-01/1569934052372.png', '9799.00', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, '<p>Ariston freestanding Tumble Dryer features: silver color. Outstanding 9kg drum&nbsp; Multi-Programs digital screen</p>\r\n\r\n<p>About the product<br />\r\nThis affordable dryer with a 9kg capacity and a variety of different drying cycles available this is an excellent choice of drying for a large family of five or more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;New Door Design</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To improve drying efficiency, the geometry of the inner profile of the glass has been completely redesigned. The new fluid-dynamic shape of the glass makes it possible to guide the garment during the movement phase, helping them move towards the inside of the drum, thereby improving the drying performance for larger quantities of laundry.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;Cupboard Program</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This drying cycle leaves 3% residual moisture in laundry and is specially designed for the most delicate garments, such as lingerie. The flow of air inside the drum and the latter&#39;s movements caress the fibers gently without damaging them.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;Fluff Filter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With the intelligent fluff filter, you are finally rid of the bothersome fluff. And in addition, the fluff filter is especially convenient. Fluff filter and laundry are kept separate at all times - guaranteeing fluff-free laundry.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;Empty Water Indicator Light</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Empty Water indicator light signals that the water container should be emptied. When it is flashing replacing the empty water container, the dryer must be running for this to happen.</p>', 'TCF 97B 6XX1 (EX)', 10, 1, 100, '2019-10-01 16:47:32', '2019-10-03 18:22:02', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
