(110, 'MICROWAVE OVENS-Ariston-MN 313 IX A', '/uploads/product/main_image/2019-10-01/1569936564889.png', '8449.00', NULL, NULL, 1, 1, '<p>ARISTON BUILT IN MICROWAVE 60 CM 22 LITER WITH GRILL MN 313 IX A</p>\r\n\r\n<p>About the product<br />\r\nThe Ariston Microwave Oven with Grill features a 1700 Watt microwave, which is ready to ease your cooking experience. This microwave oven has a generous capacity of 22L that lets you cook large quantities of meals easily. This microwave oven has eight preset programs, five power levels, two combination levels, and defrost setting dedicated to cooking different types of food at the touch of a button. The glass turntable and metal grill can be easily replaced according to your cooking preferences. The digital controls help you control the functions of this microwave grill and indulge in versatile cooking. The child lock ensures the safety of your kids while you delight in your cooking.<br />\r\nFeatures We Love&nbsp;<br />\r\nA Stylish Delight As this Ariston microwave oven and grill feature dual functionality, you can cook delicacies either way according to your food preferences for the day. You can use glass turntable when you want to go for microwave cooking or go for the metal grill when you want to treat yourself or family with some roasted or delicious grilled meals. Moreover, the 22L capacity helps you cook huge meals in lesser time.</p>', 'MN 313 IX A', 14, 1, 100, '2019-10-01 17:29:24', '2019-10-03 18:26:23', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
