(112, 'MICROWAVE OVENS-Ariston-MP 776 IX A', '/uploads/product/main_image/2019-10-01/1569937028228.png', '15899.00', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, '<p>ARISTON BUILT-IN MICROWAVE 60 CM 40 LITER WITH GRILL STAINLESS STEEL</p>\r\n\r\n<p>About the product<br />\r\nThe Ariston Microwave with Grill features a 900 Watt microwave, which is ready to ease your cooking experience. This microwave has a generous capacity of 40L that lets you cook large quantities of meals easily. This microwave has eight preset programs, five power levels, two combination levels, and defrost setting dedicated to cooking different types of food at the touch of a button. The glass turntable and metal grill can be easily replaced according to your cooking preferences. The digital controls help you control the functions of this microwave grill and indulge in versatile cooking. The child lock ensures the safety of your kids while you delight in your cooking.<br />\r\nFeatures We Love&nbsp;<br />\r\nA Stylish Delight A sleek design complemented by an easy-to-use Touch Control Interface makes the Built-In Microwave a pleasure to cook with and an attractive addition which integrates easily into every d&eacute;cor. Full Safety No matter what you cook or where you cook, one of the first and foremost things to take care of is child safety. The digital buttons of this Ariston microwave oven are easy and safe to use. When you set your food to cook in the oven, you can handle other chores in a carefree way by turning on the child safety lock. The audible signal is an add-on feature that lets you know your food has been cooked.</p>', 'MP 776 IX A', 14, 1, 100, '2019-10-01 17:37:08', '2019-10-03 18:29:33', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
