(236, 'MICROWAVE OVENS-SAMSUNG-MS23K3513AK/GY', '/uploads/product/main_image/2019-10-02/1570018223452.jpg', '3100.00', NULL, '0.00', 0, 1, '<p>Samsung microwave, 23 liters, 1150 watts of Solo. Defrost Quick Defrost<br />\r\nThanks to a new algorithm, the Quick Defrost technology significantly reduces the defrosting time required to foods while preserving the appearance and nutritional qualities.<br />\r\ndeodorization function<br />\r\nThis function allows to remove the air from the cavity to remove odors, and so keep your fresh and delicious dishes<br />\r\neco mode<br />\r\nEco Mode new Samsung microwave allows minimal power consumption in standby mode, thus reducing significantly the electricity bill.<br />\r\nOven Capacity: 23 Liter<br />\r\nSolo Microwave<br />\r\npower levels<br />\r\nElectronic Controls<br />\r\nFunctions AutoCook, Favorites, deodorization and Quick Defrost<br />\r\nSave time by taking advantage of the 5 ultra rapid thawing programs (thawed 500 g minced meat 2 minutes 30)<br />\r\nClock<br />\r\nEco mode<br />\r\nit not only offers better cooking performance but also excellent resistance to wear and abrasion, while facilitating the cleaning<br />\r\nchild Safety<br />\r\nDesign curved and blue LED display for a modern aesthetic<br />\r\nblack color.<br />\r\nNet Weight: 12 kg<br />\r\nDimensions (WxHxD): 48.9 x 27.5 x 37.4 cm<br />\r\nCavity dimensions (WxHxD): 33 x 21.1 x 32.4 cm<br />\r\nCavity: Ceramic enamel<br />\r\nPower levels: 6</p>', 'MS23K3513AK/GY', 1, 5, 100, '2019-10-02 16:10:23', '2019-10-18 01:43:30', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
(237, 'BUILT IN DISH WASHERS-SAMSUNG-VC21K5130VB/GT', '/uploads/product/main_image/2019-10-02/1570018579124.jpg', '5499.00', NULL, '0.00', 1, 1, '<p>Samsung vacuum cleaner, no bag, 2100 watts - 2 litre&nbsp;-&nbsp;blue -&nbsp;Vietnam</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The CycloneForce filter with a tangle-free turbine has a non-clogged turbine network with dust or hair. It maintains optimal cleanliness, so you won&#39;t have to waste time removing tangled hair with your hands.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Samsung VC5100 vacuum cleaner features a powerful motor and an innovative dust picking brush that sticks to the floors. It sucks dust, dirt and hair quickly and deeply without clogging, providing a high level of cleaning performance.<br />\r\nAvoids clogged hairbrush *<br />\r\nThe tangle does not get clogged due to the accumulation of pet hair as dirt enters directly into the litter box. It maintains optimal picking and cleaning performance so you don&#39;t have to waste time removing tangled hair with your hands.<br />\r\nEasy to unload the detachable box<br />\r\nThe Samsung VC5100&dagger;s simple garbage bin is easy to remove and unload. You can quickly detach it by simply pressing the button, roll the lid to open it, flip the contents into the garbage bin and then easily put it back in place.<br />\r\nLightweight, easy to transport and use<br />\r\nThanks to its light weight, you can clean every corner of the house quickly and with minimal effort. The weight of the garbage bin has been reduced by 25% *, making it easy to pull and move around the house.<br />\r\nEasy access to control buttons<br />\r\nThe remote control handle * has built-in easily accessible control buttons to quickly turn on and off the device and select the optimal suction power without stopping cleaning.<br />\r\nEasy cleaning of many different areas<br />\r\nThe 3-in-1 accessory pack provides a range of accessories to suit different cleaning needs.</p>', 'VC21K5130VB/GT', 31, 5, 100, '2019-10-02 16:16:19', '2019-10-19 16:11:07', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
(238, 'BUILT IN DISH WASHERS-SAMSUNG-VC18M31A0HP/GT', '/uploads/product/main_image/2019-10-02/1570018718651.png', '2599.00', NULL, '0.00', 0, 1, '<p>A Samsung vacuum cleaner, 1,800 watts- red - 2 litre&nbsp;- Vietnam</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The tangle-free turbine provides a more uniform * suction that does not clog the hair, maintaining the maximum suction power for a long time. * Based on test conducted by Samsung. The turbine fan was tested using a combination of human hair and pet hair on the ground. Compared to Samsung&#39;s traditional VC21F50VNAR / EV model.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The spacious garbage bin can accommodate two liters of dust and dirt, so you can clean for longer without having to empty it frequently. With a large, transparent &quot;sunroof&quot; lid, you can easily see how full the box is with a quick look and no bending.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>remote control<br />\r\nThe remote control handle * has built-in easily accessible controls, so you can quickly turn the device on and off and select the optimal suction power without stopping cleaning.</p>', 'VC18M31A0HP/GT', 31, 5, 100, '2019-10-02 16:18:38', '2019-10-19 16:12:34', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
(239, 'PowerLife Bagged-SAMSUNG-VC18M3110VB/GT', '/uploads/product/main_image/2019-10-02/1570018813271.png', '2399.00', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, '<p>Samsung vacuum cleaner, no bag, 1,800 watts, blue- 2 litre&nbsp;- Vietnam</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Greater consistency<br />\r\nTurbine prevent tangles<br />\r\nThe tangle-free turbine provides a more uniform * suction that does not clog the hair, maintaining the maximum suction power for a long time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Based on test conducted by Samsung. The turbine fan was tested using a combination of human hair and pet hair on the ground.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Easily check the inner part<br />\r\nSpacious garbage bin inside<br />\r\nThe spacious garbage bin can accommodate two liters of dust and dirt, so you can clean for longer without having to empty it frequently.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With a large, transparent &quot;sunroof&quot; lid, you can easily see how full the box is with a quick look and no bending.</p>', 'VC18M3110VB/GT', 31, 5, 100, '2019-10-02 16:20:13', '2019-10-09 13:41:47', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
(240, 'PowerLife Bagged-SAMSUNG-VC16BSNMARD/GT', '/uploads/product/main_image/2019-10-02/1570018980718.png', '2325.00', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, '<p>A Samsung - 1600 watt - red&nbsp;vacuum - 1.5 litre&nbsp;- Vietnam</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Have a good time cleaning the house, rather than shopping for bags<br />\r\nDust and pet hair can be eliminated - and dust bags. Vacuum cleaners do not pick up dust as much as bagless models, as their bags must be replaced even before the middle of the bag is full, which is neither effective nor economical. Goodbye now, with bagless vacuum cleaners you will stop looking for and spending money on the right type of bag, whether in the store or online. Above all, it is important that the vacuum cleaner clean the floors, not the wallet.<br />\r\nEffective suction power for a cleaner home<br />\r\nThanks to Samsung&#39;s Twin Chamber System &trade;, you can enjoy an improved cleaning experience with high efficiency. The cyclonic air generated in the inner chamber forces the residue of lint, sediment and all fine dust particles to enter the outer chamber and move away from the filter. This helps prevent clogging and ensures long-lasting suction power for a cleaner home.<br />\r\nEase of use and the possibility of unloading more easily<br />\r\nOnce you have cleaned the entire house with a vacuum cleaner, getting rid of any dust remaining on the floor will be the last thing you want. Just unscrew and manage the dust container to open it and empty the contents directly into the trash. Goodbye to any lost and no more chaos. The long power cable also gives you access to all aspects of the room.<br />\r\nThe NB 300 brush adjusts the airflow of the nozzle for higher suction power all the time. It is also made of special materials that prevent dust from sticking to the bottom plate, so you don&#39;t have to waste time cleaning the accessory. In addition, the brush has a soft support to protect furniture from tearing and scratching</p>', 'VC16BSNMARD/GT', 31, 5, 100, '2019-10-02 16:23:00', '2019-10-09 13:49:20', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
