(312, 'FRIDGES-SAMSUNG-RZ32M71107F + RR39M73007F', '/uploads/product/2019-10-15/1571129847222.png', '44400.00', NULL, '0.00', 0, 1, '<p>Samsung Twins Refrigerator 12 Feet Stainless Steel RZ32M71107F&amp;RR39M73007FRefrigerator 12 Feet NoFrost<br />\r\nFreezer NoFrost 6 Drawer<br />\r\nIce Maker<br />\r\nWater Dispenser<br />\r\nReversible Door<br />\r\nLed IlluminationHas a large capacity, but in a Cabinet Fit design that will fit harmoniously into your existing kitchen. There&rsquo;s plenty of room to store your weekly grocery shopping, and it&rsquo;s much easier to keep everything neatly and efficiently organized, so you can quickly find and take out the things you ne</p>\r\n\r\n<p>No Frost technology enhances the circulation of air to maintain a constant temperature in every corner of the refrigerator, which prevents the build up of frost and ice. It also reaches the target temperature much faster, increases the cooling system&rsquo;s durability, and avoids wasting power on def</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The All-around Cooling system continually monitors any temperature fluctuation and cools the fridge evenly from corner to corner. Cold air is blown out through multiple vents on every shelf level to create a multi-directional airflow, so it maintains a constant temperature and food stays fresher.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A Flat &amp; Cabinet Fit design creates a completely harmonious look that upgrades your whole kitchen. It fits seamlessly with the surface of your existing furniture, and it&rsquo;s flat front doesn&rsquo;t stick out, so you can freely open the door and use the drawers without being obstructed by the side wall.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Includes a Smart Dongle, so you can check what it&rsquo;s doing from anywhere at any time using an App* on your smartphone. You can control its Rapid Cooling modes, monitor the temperature, and receive alerts if the door is left open. And it even diagnoses errors, so you don&rsquo;t have to read the manual.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The high efficiency, long lasting LED lighting in the top of the freezer compartment is brighter and more power-efficient than conventional lighting. It illuminates every corner, so it&rsquo;s much easier to see and find ingredients, and saves money on your electricity bills.</p>', 'RZ32M71107F + RR39M73007F', 17, 5, 100, '2019-10-15 12:57:27', '2019-10-19 15:40:42', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
(313, 'FREEZERS-SAMSUNG-RZ32M71107F', '/uploads/product/2019-10-15/1571129918439.jpg', '22850.00', NULL, '0.00', 0, 1, '<p>SAMSUNG Deep Freezer RZ32M71107F Steel 11.4 ft - Color: Silver - Compressor Digital Inverter 10 years warranty - external control screen<br />\r\nDepth: 694<br />\r\nHeight: 1853 mm<br />\r\nWidth: 595 mm<br />\r\nMaterial: Metal<br />\r\nModel Number: RZ32M71107F<br />\r\nCapacity: null<br />\r\nShipping Weight: null 11.4 Cubic Feet<br />\r\nBrandSamsung<br />\r\nColor Silver<br />\r\nDepth 694<br />\r\nHeight 1853 mm<br />\r\nWidth 595 mm<br />\r\nMaterial: Metal<br />\r\nFreezer style</p>', 'RZ32M71107F', 18, 5, 100, '2019-10-15 12:58:38', '2019-10-19 15:46:41', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
(314, 'FREEZERS-SAMSUNG-RT62K7150SL/MR', '/uploads/product/2019-10-15/1571130001968.png', '29800.00', NULL, '0.00', 0, 1, '<p>Samsung Refrigerator-Silver, 594LColorSilver<br />\r\n<br />\r\nModel NumberRT58K7150SP/MR<br />\r\nCapacity26 Cubic Feet<br />\r\nStyleFreezer on Top<br />\r\nExpirable<br />\r\nSerial Scan Required<br />\r\nItem EAN2724331414753<br />\r\nWeight &amp; Dimensions<br />\r\nShipping Weight95 Kg<br />\r\nRead less<br />\r\nDESCRIPTION:<br />\r\nThe Samsung RT58K7150SP MR Refrigerator helps you keep food fresh and moisture rich even after a long time. This Samsung fridge looks elegant in silver, and it sports a minimalist design. It has a storage capacity of 580L that is ideal for storing large quantities of meals. And to hold such large amounts of ingredients safely and firmly it features toughened glass shelves that also resist heat and are safe from breakage. The fridge has a Twin Cooling system that fills its interior with cold air from top to bottom while also preserving the ingredients&#39; original aromas.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>KEY FEATURES<br />\r\nDimensions: Width: 840 mm<br />\r\nDepth: 780 mm<br />\r\nHeight: 1790 mm<br />\r\nSilver</p>', 'RT62K7150SL/MR', 17, 5, 100, '2019-10-15 13:00:01', '2019-10-19 15:51:08', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
(315, 'FRIDGES-SAMSUNG-RT62K7000SP/MR', '/uploads/product/2019-10-15/1571130069439.png', '28700.00', NULL, '0.00', 0, 1, '<p>Samsung Refrigerator 27 Feet Digital Twin Cooling Silver RT62K7000Model RT62K7000SP<br />\r\nSize 26 feet<br />\r\nColor Silver<br />\r\nNo Frost&nbsp;<br />\r\nLiters 620<br />\r\nDigital&nbsp;<br />\r\nDispenser No<br />\r\nShelves Tempered Glass<br />\r\nWarrantee 10 Years<br />\r\nPlasma No<br />\r\nWidth 836 mm<br />\r\nDepth 788 mm<br />\r\nHeight 1862 mm<br />\r\nThe MT12 brings inventive and convenient features to your kitchen with new energy-efficient cooling technology. The Digital Inverter Compressor adjusts the temperature of the fridge based on how you use it to keep the fridge at a consistent cool temperature, lowering energy consumption. Place meat, fruits and veggies in the convenient CoolSelect Turbo compartment to keep them at their optimal temperature for the freshest taste. The MT12 makes saving energy and keeping food fresh easier than ever.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Energy efficiency that makes the grade<br />\r\nSamsung&rsquo;s innovative Digital Inverter Compressor helps preserve your grocery items &mdash; and the environment. The Digital Inverter Compressor maintains consistent refrigerator cooling by adjusting its settings based on humidity levels and usage patterns, which saves up to 20% more energy than conventional compressors. Not only did the Digital Inverter Compressor&rsquo;s efficiency help earn the MT12 refrigerator an Energy A rating, it means less wear and, ultimately, greater fridge reliability.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>One compartment, three optimised settings<br />\r\nThe MT12 has a Coolselect Turbo compartment that understands the difference between food groups &mdash; it offers the optimal pre-set cooling modes for meats, fruits and vegetables. Use Fresh Mode to chill juicy bunches of grapes at 3&ordm;C, or select Soft Freeze Mode (-5C) to store succulent lamb chops without fear of freezer burn. And if your freezer is already packed, simply set the compartment to Freeze Mode (-12&ordm;C) to preserve healthy greens such as broccoli and spinach for later enjoyment.<br />\r\nSeparate sensors ensure ideal temperatures</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Whether you&rsquo;re storing meats in the freezer or vegetables in the refrigerator, Samsung&rsquo;s dual sensor system helps ensure chops won&rsquo;t get freezer burn, and lettuce won&rsquo;t spoil as quickly. Separate sensors in the refrigerator and freezer compartments independently monitor and optimise temperature and humidity settings for ideal cooling levels &mdash; so all food items remain in peak condition, longer.<br />\r\nSimple inner wall design increases capacity</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When it comes to maximising the capacity of the MT12 Refrigerator, no detail is overlooked, including the ductwork. Slim, non-protruding ducts and shelves that rest on grooves instead of notches free up more space for storing food. Not only do these improvements help create a more spacious interior than in conventional refrigerators, the simple inner wall design lends an elegant touch.<br />\r\nA slim dispenser with modern flair</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Enjoy the convenience and functionality of an external water dispenser without having to compromise the aesthetic of your kitchen decor. With no protruding elements, the slim dispenser is inset to maintain the refrigerator&rsquo;s sleek surface. It&rsquo;s so attractive you&rsquo;ll want to raise a glass of chilled water to its sophisticated style.<br />\r\nCool, bright and energy saving LED light</p>\r\n\r\n<p>See a difference inside the refrigerator &mdash; and on your electric bill &mdash; with LED lighting. Strategically placed on the interior sides, the LED lights illuminate every corner with a brilliancy that&rsquo;s less harsh and uses up to 75% less energy than conventional light bulbs. LED lighting also emits less heat than conventional bulbs, so the refrigerator doesn&rsquo;t have to work as hard to compensate.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nDigital Display<br />\r\nThe external touch display lets you set cooling modes without having to open the door. Conveniently change temperature settings with just the push of a button. As sleek as the refrigerator itself, the display&rsquo;s modern sophistication is perfect for today&rsquo;s kitchen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br />\r\nNew Shelf Design<br />\r\nWhen it comes to beauty, it&rsquo;s what&rsquo;s inside that counts. Complementing the MT12 interior&rsquo;s clean design and the exterior&rsquo;s stainless steel finish are silver metallic-trimmed shelves. Whether the refrigerator is fully stocked or not, you&rsquo;ll see the new shelf design shine with sophistication.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nAdjustable Guard<br />\r\nAdjustable guards allow flexible storage on both the refrigerator and freezer doors. Guards shift up and down to accommodate items of various sizes in both compartments. Store bottled beverages and other tall items upright, and still have room for other products like yogurt or ice pop molds.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', 'RT62K7000SP/MR', 17, 5, 100, '2019-10-15 13:01:09', '2019-10-19 15:54:27', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
(316, 'FRIDGES-SAMSUNG-RT58K7150SP/MR', '/uploads/product/2019-10-15/1571130166954.png', '28200.00', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, '<p>Samsung Refrigerator 25 Feet Digital Twin Cooling With Dispenser RT58K7150The Samsung RT58K7150SP MR Refrigerator helps you keep food fresh and moisture rich even after a long time. This Samsung fridge looks elegant in silver, and it sports a minimalist design. It has a storage capacity of 580L that is ideal for storing large quantities of meals. And to hold such large amounts of ingredients safely and firmly it features toughened glass shelves that also resist heat and are safe from breakage. The fridge has a Twin Cooling system that fills its interior with cold air from top to bottom while also preserving the ingredients&#39; original aromas.<br />\r\nKEY FEATURES<br />\r\nDimensions: Width: 840 mm<br />\r\nDepth: 780 mm<br />\r\nHeight: 1790 mm<br />\r\nSilver<br />\r\nMOISTURE-FULL FRESHNESS ALL OVER THE FRIDGE<br />\r\nOnly Twin Cooling Plus&trade; creates a favorable environment for preserving fresh food in the fridge with 70% humidity, compared to 30% in a conventional TMF. So it keeps ingredients fresh for longer without drying out. * Based on internal testing comparing Samsung models RT22SCSW2 and RT7000K.Provides the ultimate in flexible storage. Easily convert your freezer into a fridge to keep all the fresh food you need to store for different seasons or special occasions. Or switch to off* mode to save energy. * The temperature of the compartments remains under 15℃ using low electricity<br />\r\nDigital Inverter Technology automatically adjusts the compressor speed in response to cooling demand across 7 levels. It uses less energy, minimizes noise and reduces wear and tear for longer-lasting performance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'RT58K7150SP/MR', 17, 5, 100, '2019-10-15 13:02:46', '2019-10-15 13:02:46', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL),
